Chokers - by EDG

Be REALLY careful with the weight of this LoRA. Less than 0.7!

Training for accessories is extremely difficult but somehow I made it work.

It works especially well on anime checkpoints.

Not so much on realistic ones, but we'll figure this out later.

Check my prompts for guidance on LoRA weights.

HAVE FUN!
